{"tid":1798253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候要諗下1月11日台灣大選結果出咗之後點樣做文宣","createTime":"2019-12-26T06:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T17:19:28.000Z","uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7d62994830ded68f0a1fc173da7c7c8d76b9ea","tid":1798253,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"蔡英文好可能大勝韓國瑜<br />\n到時文宣方向可以係, 舉例︰<br />\n維尼無能，捧件垃圾韓國瑜出黎, 連蔡英文呢個上任頭幾年比台灣人鬧佢無貢獻既總統都可以連任<br />\n再睇返維尼在任7-8年, 一事無成<br />\n甚麼2025, 一帶一路, 雄安新區, 上海深圳澳門金融業開放, 香港、台灣全部失敗, 劣跡斑斑<br />\n究竟維尼係咪臥底？<br />\n加上呢幾年中共不斷指民進黨蔡英文係台獨，成日文攻武嚇<br />\n如果蔡英文連任, 維尼唔敢有任何動作, 又可以笑佢無能, 原來一直得個up字<br />\n以上文宣方向主要針對大陸人"},{"pid":"530f922fae7b880fe14b10b7f50f4acd99e4ed08","tid":1798253,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ecf3be2eef78062920bef6eb72c4ea8f0e4f85","tid":1798253,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:35:06.000Z","msg":"Pull"},{"pid":"28960596451a1d2561bf63223ca7e3e0967d29a6","tid":1798253,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"方向正確"},{"pid":"5f5a9fb318df189ffd5289c1a5112377b872c9f9","tid":1798253,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541020a3687f86ca6b32f248651f4353331dc84f","tid":1798253,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"登廣告頭版恭喜蔡英文連任台灣國總統有冇得諗?"},{"pid":"ac21053018dad712631428b03871cd1e6b491139","tid":1798253,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c31b82b392ab9e76867a232c7b715a1fe574352a","tid":1798253,"uid":56043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:53:02.000Z","ms